member.name: TfActiveSelEnd
member.summary: Elements of the TfActiveSelEnd enumeration specify which end of a selected range of text is active.

member.name: TfActiveSelEnd.TF_AE_NONE
member.summary: The selected range has no active end. This is typical for selected ranges other than the default selected range.

member.name: TfActiveSelEnd.TF_AE_START
member.summary: The active end is at the start of the selected range.

member.name: TfActiveSelEnd.TF_AE_END
member.summary: The active end is at the end of the selected range.
